ActImmigration and Refugee Protection Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Immigration and Refugee Protection Regulations
PrecisRegulations amending the IMMIGRATION AND REFUGEE PROTECTION REGULATIONS in order to (1) ensure consistent application of the new provision among applicable decision-makers; and (2) make technical amendments to align the Immigration and Refugee Protection Regulations and Immigration and Refugee Protection Act.
